483
00:31:14,039 --> 00:31:16,208
To show off my house.

484
00:31:16,917 --> 00:31:18,127
It's nice, isn't it?

485
00:31:18,919 --> 00:31:19,753
Yes, it is.

486
00:31:20,754 --> 00:31:23,799
Jeez, you don't even understand a joke.

487
00:31:23,882 --> 00:31:26,510
It'll only cause a scandal
if people see us together in public.

488
00:31:30,848 --> 00:31:31,849
So, what's this about?

489
00:31:31,932 --> 00:31:34,059
You said I was like bad luck to you,
so I didn't expect to see you again.

490
00:31:34,643 --> 00:31:35,978
I never said you were bad luck.

491
00:31:37,021 --> 00:31:38,564
