you want to know about him?

498
00:32:05,215 --> 00:32:06,592
Anyway,

499
00:32:07,551 --> 00:32:10,179
I asked you here
because I felt a bit of responsibility.

500
00:32:10,262 --> 00:32:12,890
I saw you issued a correction
about the Yoon Jung-ho article.

501
00:32:12,973 --> 00:32:14,308
Did he say he'd drop the lawsuit?

502
00:32:17,269 --> 00:32:18,896
