515
00:33:02,106 --> 00:33:03,440
I issued a correction

516
00:33:04,024 --> 00:33:06,151
and corrected my mistake as a reporter.

517
00:33:06,235 --> 00:33:07,194
I won't apologize personally.

518
00:33:08,612 --> 00:33:10,114
-Look--
-I'll make sure

519
00:33:10,197 --> 00:33:11,824
that you're not affected by this.

520
00:33:12,408 --> 00:33:14,535
-That's not the point--
-If we're done here,

521
00:33:15,327 --> 00:33:16,286
I'll be on my way.

522
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:18,664
But…

